    "It can be seen that many lowlevel principles are summarized in the high-level principles of Justice, Explicability, and Non-maleficence.",
    "Figure 8 shows a count of tools by type (three macro categories as described in the methodology section) for each stage in the life cycle addressed by the tool.",
